expense with respect to option rights granted to eligible employees amounted to $79.5 million at December 31, 2021. The
unrecognized compensation expense is being amortized on a straight-line basis over the three-year vesting period, net of estimated
forfeitures based on historical activity, and is expected to be recognized over a weighted-average period of 1.09 years.
